node.title: Gunshot mystery: Probe after shots fired in WhangƒÅrei, 'too early to say' if gang-related
node.description: It comes after six gang members were arrested following "ongoing tensions" in the area earlier this month.
node.content: ["An investigation is underway after a gunshot was reportedly fired in the Whang\u0101rei suburb of Raumanga on Wednesday morning.\n", "Emergency services were called about 9:20am to Mahanga Pl after reports of a gun going off. However, police didn't find anyone injured.\u00a0\u00a0", "A police spokesperson says it's too early to say if the incident is related to recent gang tensions in the area.\u00a0", "In the meantime, the spokesperson says officers are investigating and an update will be provided later.", "Earlier this month, six gang members and associates were arrested in Northland following \"ongoing tensions\" between the Head Hunters and Black Power.\u00a0"]
